# Target modern browsers only - no legacy polyfills needed
# This targets browsers that support ES6+ features natively

# Production browsers
last 2 Chrome versions
last 2 Firefox versions
last 2 Safari versions
last 2 Edge versions

# Mobile browsers
last 2 ChromeAndroid versions
last 2 iOS versions

# Exclude old browsers
not dead
not ie 11
not op_mini all
not samsung < 15
not and_uc < 15

# Minimum browser versions that support modern JavaScript
Chrome >= 80
Firefox >= 75
Safari >= 13.1
Edge >= 80